---
title: Double Lamb Rump & Parsnip Mash with Creamy Honey Mustard Sauce
description: What's the secret to moist, tender and extra-tasty lamb? Use a cut with the cap of fat still on, so the meat stays juicy while roasting. Bring
extra flavour with a creamy honey mustard sauce, plus some parsnip mash and you've got a restaurant-quality dish made by yours truly.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/double-lamb-rump-parsnip-mash-c0643f2c.jpg
